name: Early Ai Art by Kevin Page

metadata.name: Picasso's Brother
metadata.description:
What if Picasso had a half-brother who was a hypnotist? Perhaps he would steal Pablo's paintings to use as hypnotic objects?

"Picasso's Brother" is a mirco-length Ai-generated art film that tells the story of the brother Picasso never had, a hypnotist and lover who was tragically involved with a Russian dancer, a story of romance and betrayal that never was...

Original 1/1 Ai art film (1280x720 px, 48 seconds) with original soundtrack by the artist.

For more on #AiArt and the #NFTcommunity FOLLOW @KevinWPage on Twitter.
